message:
Command `cd /workspace/SheepVibes && git commit -m "fix: make createFeedWidget return widget element

- Modified createFeedWidget to return the created widget instead of appending it
- Updated loadFeedsForTab to append the returned widget to the DOM
- This resolves the critical runtime error where widget.replaceWith(newWidget) was failing because newWidget was undefined

Co-authored-by: openhands <openhands@all-hands.dev>"` executed with exit code 0.
